  dialogPieces:
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 5503601100735391139, guid: b76abf6cea25fbc4c811a4099ea1b24a, type: 3}
    text: "There\u2019s another letter at the door."
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 5503601100735391139, guid: b76abf6cea25fbc4c811a4099ea1b24a, type: 3}
    text: "I thought there wouldn\u2019t be any more after yesterday."
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 5503601100735391139, guid: b76abf6cea25fbc4c811a4099ea1b24a, type: 3}
    text: But it still came.
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: -6470460504253458178, guid: 6a6bd0dba60404a4abe76b8e2ee510e4, type: 3}
    text: "It\u2019s as if something\u2026 still isn\u2019t over."
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 5503601100735391139, guid: b76abf6cea25fbc4c811a4099ea1b24a, type: 3}
    text: "\u2026Let\u2019s open it."
